name: Shim F Big Book Sponsorship
description: A recovering sexaholic shares how he found a new and sober way of life through the time tested wisdom found in the Big Book of Alcoholics Anonymous in this in depth big book study. The original files for this collection of episodes can be found on Google Drive: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1CT5PSSjgjwiRbPb6mZEcS2jtRlIbp1A3 This podcast contains a complete series of recordings, no new episodes are expected.
